Scott Dominic PALMATEER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Nicole Jean PALMATEER, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0054 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 15, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Nicole Jean Palmateer's notice of voluntary dismissal of cross-appeal is granted, and the cross-appeal is dismissed. The appeal remains pending.
